{"image_id": "OXY_2014_page_70", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "56", "bbox": [608.6, 1547.3, 629.4, 1570.4]}, {"text": "Derivatives Not Designated as Hedging Instruments", "bbox": [75.0, 70.5, 535.3, 93.6]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes Occidental's net volumes of outstanding commodity derivatives contracts not designated", "bbox": [112.5, 94.9, 1168.3, 117.0]}, {"text": "as hedging instruments, including both financial and physical derivative contracts as of December 31, 2014 and 2013:", "bbox": [75.0, 118.7, 1104.0, 140.8]}, {"text": "Net Outstanding Position", "bbox": [950.2, 160.8, 1134.2, 183.4]}, {"text": "Long / (Short)", "bbox": [990.3, 180.6, 1089.6, 203.2]}, {"text": "Commodity", "bbox": [450.8, 211.8, 532.9, 234.5]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [958.3, 211.8, 994.4, 234.5]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [1085.4, 211.8, 1121.5, 234.5]}, {"text": "Oil (million barrels)", "bbox": [81.3, 240.9, 216.5, 263.6]}, {"text": "(9)", "bbox": [1015.9, 240.9, 1035.8, 263.6]}, {"text": "(22)", "bbox": [1134.0, 240.9, 1163.0, 263.6]}, {"text": "Natural gas (billion cubic feet)", "bbox": [81.3, 268.0, 295.1, 290.7]}, {"text": "(32)", "bbox": [1006.9, 268.0, 1035.9, 290.7]}, {"text": "(10)", "bbox": [1134.0, 268.0, 1163.0, 290.7]}, {"text": "CO2 (million cubic feet)", "bbox": [81.3, 295.1, 246.8, 317.8]}, {"text": "621", "bbox": [1003.3, 295.1, 1030.4, 317.8]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [1141.3, 295.1, 1157.5, 317.8]}, {"text": "The volumes in the table above exclude contracts tied to index prices, for which the fair value, if any, is minimal at any", "bbox": [112.5, 348.3, 1168.4, 370.4]}, {"text": "point in time.  These contracts do not expose Occidental to price risk because the contract prices fluctuate with index prices.", "bbox": [75.0, 372.1, 1159.7, 394.2]}, {"text": "Occidental fulfills its short positions through its own production or by third-party purchase contracts.  Subsequent to", "bbox": [112.5, 395.9, 1168.3, 418.0]}, {"text": "December 31, 2014, Occidental entered into purchase contracts for a substantial portion of the outstanding positions at year-", "bbox": [75.0, 419.6, 1162.8, 441.7]}, {"text": "end and has sufficient production capacity and the ability to enter into additional purchase contracts to satisfy the remaining", "bbox": [75.0, 443.4, 1168.4, 465.5]}, {"text": "positions.", "bbox": [75.0, 467.1, 169.7, 489.2]}, {"text": "Approximately $71 million net loss and $11 million net gain from derivatives not designated as hedging instruments were", "bbox": [112.5, 490.9, 1167.9, 513.0]}, {"text": "recognized in net sales for the years ended December 31, 2014 and 2013, respectively.", "bbox": [75.0, 514.6, 840.6, 536.7]}, {"text": "Fair Value of Derivatives", "bbox": [75.0, 564.0, 296.4, 587.1]}, {"text": "The following table presents the gross and net fair values of Occidental’s outstanding derivatives as of December 31, 2014", "bbox": [108.4, 588.4, 1168.3, 610.5]}, {"text": "and 2013:", "bbox": [75.0, 612.2, 163.1, 634.3]}, {"text": "(in millions)", "bbox": [81.3, 655.3, 163.3, 678.0]}, {"text": "December 31, 2014", "bbox": [81.3, 705.3, 227.5, 728.0]}, {"text": "Asset Derivatives", "bbox": [421.0, 685.5, 560.9, 708.2]}, {"text": "Balance Sheet Location", "bbox": [397.1, 705.3, 580.3, 728.0]}, {"text": "Fair", "bbox": [689.5, 685.5, 719.3, 708.2]}, {"text": "Value", "bbox": [683.2, 705.3, 726.5, 728.0]}, {"text": "Liability Derivatives", "bbox": [838.7, 685.5, 991.2, 708.2]}, {"text": "Balance Sheet Location", "bbox": [823.4, 705.3, 1006.5, 728.0]}, {"text": "Fair", "bbox": [1110.6, 685.5, 1140.3, 708.2]}, {"text": "Value", "bbox": [1104.2, 705.3, 1147.5, 728.0]}, {"text": "Cash-flow hedges (a)", "bbox": [81.3, 736.6, 228.6, 759.2]}, {"text": "Commodity contracts", "bbox": [106.3, 785.4, 258.7, 808.1]}, {"text": "Other current assets", "bbox": [327.2, 765.7, 474.3, 788.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [671.1, 765.7, 680.1, 788.4]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [722.4, 765.7, 738.6, 788.4]}, {"text": "Acc